 NOTES AND ASSUMPTIONS:-

 Imported randint method form random
 to generate random integer

 For the Password generator make sure to enter the length greater than or equal to 8.
 
 For Password validater: 

 Arguments:
 	password (string)
 Return:
 	result (string): either "Secure", "Insecure" or "Invalid"

 Used methods
 str.isupper()
 str.islower()
 str.isdigit()

 Used lists
 forbidden_characters
 Special_characters

There are three returns for validater function:
If the given password is Invalid then function call will end after returning Invalid string 
and if it's not a Invalid password then function call will continue
If the password is not Invalid then it will check for all secure password condition and if it 
satisfies all the conditions of secure then function call will end after returning Secure string
If the password doesn't satisfies both Invalid and Secure password then there will be check for 
Insecure condition if the conditions sstisfies then function call will end after returning Insecure string

For Password generator:

Arguments:
	n (integer): 
		length of the password to generate
Return:
	secure_password (string) or 
	message that n is less then 8

Used methods
randint()

Used lists
Special_characters
digit

There are two returns for generator function:
If the given length of password is less then 8 then the fuction call will end after returning
the message that the length is less then 8